1. *Duhovi* su me plašili kada sam bio mali. (The *ghosts* used to scare me when I was a child.)
2. Videla sam *duhove* u staroj napuštenoj kući. (I saw *ghosts* in an old abandoned house.)
3. Pojedini ljudi veruju da postoje *duhovi* mrtvih ljudi. (Some people believe that there are *spirits* of dead people.)
4. Ova knjiga govori o različitim vrstama *duhova*. (This book is about different types of *ghosts*.)
5. Kada je vetrovito, često čujem *duhove* kako šuškaju kroz drveće. (When it's windy, I often hear *spirits* rustling through the trees.)
6. Pokušavam da ignorišem *duhove* svoje prošlosti. (I'm trying to ignore the *ghosts* of my past.)
7. *Duhovi* su jedna od najpopularnijih tema horor filmova. (Ghosts are one of the most popular themes of horror movies.)
8. Neki ljudi se boje da će ostati zarobljeni kao *duhovi* nakon smrti. (Some people are afraid that they will be trapped as *spirits* after death.)
9. Ovo mesto je opsednuto *duhovima* i trebalo bi ga izbegavati. (This place is haunted by *ghosts* and should be avoided.)
10. Nikada nisam video *duhove*, ali sam čuo mnoge priče o njima. (I have never seen *ghosts*, but I have heard many stories about them.)